type: txt
default: "pass"
syntax:expression: $VAR(@) in "drop", "sdrop", "alert", "pass";
                   "Action must be \"drop\", \"sdrop\", \"alert\", or \"pass\""
help: Set Snort IDP action for packets matching other rules
comp_help:Possible completions:
  drop          Drop the packet and generate an alert
  sdrop         Silently drop the packet
  alert         Generate an alert and let the packet pass
  pass          Let the packet pass and do nothing
